@JwtAuthMicroservice_HostAddress = http://localhost:5182

### Login with demo credentials
POST {{JwtAuthMicroservice_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "kavya",
  "password": "Password@123"
}

### Protected route without a token (401)
GET {{JwtAuthMicroservice_HostAddress}}/api/secure/data

### Protected route with the token received from login (200)
GET {{JwtAuthMicroservice_HostAddress}}/api/secure/data
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
